sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant Network

    User->>Client: Send Message
    Client->>Network: Attempt to send message
    alt Network is available
        Network->>Server: Deliver message
        Server-->>Client: Acknowledge receipt
        Client-->>User: Confirm delivery
    else Network is intermittent
        Network-->>Client: Delivery failed
        Client-->>User: Notify delivery failure
        Client->>Network: Retry sending message
        Network->>Server: Deliver message
        Server-->>Client: Acknowledge receipt
        Client-->>User: Confirm delivery
    end